link: Seiichi Manyama, Table of n, a(n) for n = 0..1000
formula: a(n) = -Sum_{k=0..n-1} sigma(n-k)*a(k) for n>0 with a(0) = 1.
G.f.: 1/(1 + Sum_{k>=1} k*x^k/(1 - x^k)). - _Ilya Gutkovskiy_, Oct 18 2018
program: (PARI) lista(nn) = {va = vector(nn); va[1] = 1; for (n=1, nn-1, va[n+1] = -sum(k=0, n-1, sigma(n-k)*va[k+1]);); va;} \\ _Michel Marcus_, Mar 05 2017
